===Verb===
{{en-verb}}
# (''transitive'') To transit the matter from a [[solid]] state to a [[liquid]] state usually by heat.
# (''intransitive'') To change (become transitted) from a solid state to a liquid state. 
#: ''The snowman will disappear, he will '''melt'''.''
# {{Colloquial}}To [[dissolve]].
# {{Colloquial}}To be very hot and sweating profusely.
#:''Help me!  I'm '''melting'''!''

